  "description": {
    "zh": "我们现在把这一套全收尾了，是时候把挑战升级一点了。准备好了吗？\n\n如果猎人（Jaeger）还没给你安排过类似的活儿，那这任务正好是个练手的好机会，等你完成了再来感谢我也不迟。这次的任务是清除一批Scav，但你不能用任何医疗物品，而且自己还不能受太重的伤。记得，回来时人得是活的！\n\n我可不会替你报销医疗费，所以建议你一口气干净利落地搞定，否则你收获的可能只有脑震荡和一堆赔本账，明白了吗？好，那就祝你好运，士兵。",
    "en": "Let's get all this stuff out of the way now, time to step this up a bit. Are you ready?\n\nIn case jaeger didn't give you any challenges like that, this will be a great way to prepare for that, thank me later. You need to take out a few bandits, but you aren't allowed to use some form of injurty treatment, and you can't get seriously hurt while doing that. I expect to see you still alive later!\n\nI won't be paying any hospital bills, so I suggest you do this in one clean run, otherwise you're gonna end up with a big headache and a lot less money, understand? Very well then, good luck soldier."
  },
